WEBVTT

16:25.950 --> 16:26.640 line:80%
Changyu,

16:27.200 --> 16:29.200 line:80%
why open up right after the wedding?

16:29.240 --> 16:30.650 line:80%
Why not rest more at home?

16:30.970 --> 16:32.610 line:80%
I want to earn more money

16:32.640 --> 16:34.850 line:80%
to get my parents' pig shed
running again soon,

16:34.850 --> 16:36.050 line:80%
so I have to work hard.
